  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Interest of treatment of polytraumatisms with corticoids (hydrocortisone) for patient with
      relative adrenocortical insufficiency on frequency of nosocomial infection, and hemodynamic
      complications and organs injuries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
